Package com.salesforce.dva.argus.sdk

Contains the set of Java services used to interact with Argus.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AlertService
    Provides methods to manage alerts in Argus.
    AnnotationService
    Provides methods to manipulate annotation events.
    ArgusService
    Provides read and write access to Argus.
    ArgusService.PutResult
    Represents the result of a write operation for annotations and metrics.
    AuditService
    Provides methods to manipulate annotation events.
    AuthService
    Provides methods to authenticate to Argus.
    BatchService
    Provides methods to manipulate batches.
    DashboardService
    Provides methods to manipulate dashboards.
    DiscoveryService
    Provides methods to discover metric schema.
    HistoryService
    Provides methods to retrieve entity change history.
    MetricService
    Provides methods to manipulate metrics.
    NamespaceService
    Provides methods to manipulate metrics.
    UserService
    Provides methods to manipulate users.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    DiscoveryService.FieldSelector
    Specifies the field for which to return values from for discovery service methods that return a list of field values.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    ArgusServiceException
    Exception class for the Argus SDK.
